Title: Fixed possible "omd backup" error when persisted sections change during backup
Level: 1
Component: omd
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
State: unknown
Version: 1.6.0b1
Date: 1547802040

When persisted sections of Check_MK in `var/check_mk/persisted/*` and
`var/check_mk/persisted_sections/*` vanished during the backup, the backup
job could fail in previous versions.
